pageContext.claim: “By the way, World Trade Organization, it made China. China made themselves. They did a good job. But they ripped off our country for years, and with our money and World Trade Organization backing. They went up like a rocket ship. They were flat-lined for 100 years.”
pageContext.analysis: This is false. China's economy grew rapidly well before it joined the WTO in 2001 and so it was not "flat-lined for 100 years."
